results.finalText:
**Soroban build/test/deploy workflow** (from `skills.stellar-dev.smart-contracts` sections):

**Setup**  
`stellar contract init my-contract` → edit `Cargo.toml` (cdylib + soroban-sdk 25 + testutils feature + release profile).

**Test**  
```rust
#[test]
fn test_increment() {
    let env = Env::default(); env.mock_all_auths();
    let admin = Address::generate(&env);
    let id = env.register(CounterContract, (admin.clone(),));
    let client = CounterContractClient::new(&env, &id);
    assert_eq!(client.increment(), 1);
}
```

**Build / Deploy / Invoke**  
```bash
stellar contract build
stellar keys generate --global alice --network testnet --fund
stellar contract deploy --wasm .../my_contract.wasm --source alice --network testnet -- --admin alice
stellar contract invoke --id CONTRACT_ID --source alice --network testnet -- increment
```

